{"id":299962,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-陈光诚亲友北京讨说法六人遭保安殴打后/","date":"2013-06-20T18:47:57Z","modified":"2013-06-20T18:47:57Z","title":"维权网 | 陈光诚亲友北京讨说法六人遭保安殴打后被警方带走（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日下午</span><span>，进京讨说法的陈光诚亲友在国家信访局</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>人遭保安暴力殴打，卢秋梅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>个月大的女儿受到严重惊吓。警察到场后不但不追究打人者，反而将被打者带到派出所问讯。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>据了解，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日陈光诚的大哥陈光福和卢秋梅等亲友是按照昨天国家信访局的要求来求见郭守松司长的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div><span>陈光福和卢秋梅进入办公区办理登记约见郭守松司长的手续，卢秋梅委托徐大丽照看自己</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>个月大的女儿。因天气炎热等候时间较长孩子开始哭闹，负责照看孩子的徐大丽请求保安帮忙叫出卢秋梅因而惹怒他们，几名保安不由分说上来就动手殴打几位在外等候的朋友。卢秋梅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>个月的女儿受到严重的惊吓，不停的哭闹。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>葛志慧、杨秋雨、王玉琴、徐大丽、郭帮卿、黄永璨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>人被殴打，警察到场后，不但没有追究打人者的责任，反而将陪同陈光福前来的葛志慧等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>位被保安殴打的亲友带到派出所问讯。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>截至本网发稿时，葛志慧等被保安殴打后带到派出所问讯的几位朋友仍然被关在派出所内。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>陈光福：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18315756657   </span></div>\n<div><span>卢秋梅：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13666395696   </span></div>\n<div><span>被殴打者葛志慧等人：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13261499836</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15001165132</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15810916791</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13240155083</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p><span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-g6Tbcu3A0gM/UcMjeyDzjVI/AAAAAAAAjzo/f56t2XMkJQw/s1600/v.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-g6Tbcu3A0gM/UcMjeyDzjVI/AAAAAAAAjzo/f56t2XMkJQw/s320/v.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p><span><br /></span>图：陈光福、卢秋梅及她</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>个月大的女儿张恪瑞，小娃娃已经第五次随母亲赴京上访了（照片由胡佳提供）</span><br /><span><br /></span></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}